OL,3,CBrother of Israeli hostage on hope of
OL,4,Cbringing hostages home
OL,6,FGuy Gilboa Dalal and his brother Gal
OL,7,Fboth attended the Nova music festival
OL,8,Fon October 7 when Hamas gunmen swarmed
OL,9,Fthe area, as ITV News Senior
OL,10,FInternational Correspondent John
OL,11,FIrvine reports.
OL,13,FWords by ITV News Senior Foreign
OL,14,FEditor John Angier
OL,16,FWhen Guy Gilboa Dalal announced he was
OL,17,Fgoing to the Nova music festival, his
OL,18,Folder brother Gal decided to go with
OL,19,Fhim.
