OL,3,CBrother of Israeli hostage on hope of
OL,4,Cbringing hostages home
OL,6,F"I don't think anyone else can relate
OL,7,Fto what we're going through. I feel
OL,8,Flike every day we go through the same
OL,9,Fprocess, of losing faith, losing hope,
OL,10,Ffinding it again, thinking about Guy,
OL,11,Fgetting stronger for him," said Gal.
OL,13,F"I go to sleep with him, I wake up
OL,14,Fwith him. I can actually hear his
OL,15,Fscreaming from the tunnels, telling me
OL,16,Fif I did enough today, what I'm doing
OL,17,Fto help him get out of there. As long
OL,18,Fas I'm here, I'm his voice and I have
OL,19,Fno other option than do everything I
OL,20,Fcan for him."
