OL,6,FGuy's condition is now unknown. He was
OL,7,Flast seen alive in February, when
OL,8,FHamas took him and his best friend,
OL,9,FEvyatar David, to watch other
OL,10,Fhostages, their friends, being
OL,11,Freleased. They had been tricked into
OL,12,Fbelieving that they, too, were going
OL,13,Fto be freed. A Hamas propaganda video
OL,14,Fshows them in the back of a car,
OL,15,Fgaunt, shaven-headed, pleading to be
OL,16,Fsaved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
