OL,3,CBrother of Israeli hostage on hope of
OL,4,Cbringing hostages home
OL,6,F"That was the first time they were
OL,7,Ftaken out of the tunnels in 400 days.
OL,8,FThey were staying in the same small,
OL,9,Fnarrow tunnel, unable to move, with
OL,10,Fthe same light, so they don't know
OL,11,Fwhen it's day or when it's night.
OL,12,FThey're abused on a daily basis,
OL,13,Fthey're getting a lot of beatings,
OL,14,Fthey're always hungry."
OL,16,FGal says Hamas inflicted further
OL,17,Fpsychological torture on Guy by
OL,18,Ftelling him that Gal himself is dead.
