OL,11,FHe has travelled the world with other
OL,12,Frelatives of hostages to raise support
OL,13,Ffor the Bring Them Home Now campaign.
OL,14,FIsrael says 50 hostages remain in
OL,15,FGaza, 20 thought to be alive, 30 dead.
OL,17,FAs Israel and Hamas inch towards a new
OL,18,Fceasefire, Gal's hopes are rising. But
OL,19,Feven if Guy is released, he will
OL,20,Fcontinue to campaign for the remaining
OL,21,Fcaptives.
